# Google Drive & OAuth Configurations

# 1. Google OAuth Client ID (VITE_ requires it to be bundled to the frontend for Google Sign-In)
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID="YOUR_OAUTH_CLIENT_ID"

# 2. Google Drive API Key (NO VITE_ prefix means this ONLY lives securely inside the Netlify Backend environment! Safe.)
GOOGLE_DRIVE_API_KEY="YOUR_DRIVE_API_KEY"
